I"<h3 id="1-mac-os">1. Mac OS</h3>
<h4 id="11-brew">1.1 Brew</h4>
<p>the missing package manager for macos, 和centos下的yumhe ubuntu下的apt-get类似</p>
<ol>
  <li>brew的安装目录在/usr/local/Cellar</li>
  <li>配置目录在/usr/local/etc</li>
  <li>命令目录在/usr/local/bin</li>
</ol>

<h4 id="使用">使用</h4>
<ol>
  <li>brew install boost-python</li>
  <li>brew upgrade boost</li>
  <li>brew info boost  查看boost相关信息</li>
  <li>brew link</li>
</ol>

